I'll answer his questions.

24:41.235 --> 24:45.228
Don't go anywhere.
I'm gonna need you here.

24:46.774 --> 24:47.774
Now,

24:48.555 --> 24:51.393
Here's the situation that we got here.

24:51.493 --> 24:55.312
Bring your man D'Alli in.
He'll understand the numbers.

24:57.518 --> 25:01.533
