25:30.028 --> 25:33.532
To the efforts of one man who went out there,

25:33.632 --> 25:36.472
who went out there in the cold,

25:36.572 --> 25:39.672
who was out there day and night,

25:39.772 --> 25:44.242
speaking the word, spreading the word.

25:44.342 --> 25:46.993
And the word was Teamsters.

25:48.002 --> 25:50.835
The word was unity.

25:53.240 --> 25:56.091
And it overcame the scabs.

25:56.191 --> 25:59.129
And it overcame the company.

25:59.229 --> 26:02.842
It made the day, and it made us our contract.

26:08.155 --> 26:10.607
Here's the man who led us through that fight,

26:10.707 --> 26:16.242
the man who beat Kreger,
who broke them down and who took us in,

26:16.342 --> 26:18.878
our new business manager,

26:18.978 --> 26:20.991
Red Bennett.

26:33.180 --> 26:36.877
